{"book": 24, "chapter": 22, "sections": [{"type": "heading", "heading": "耶利米給猶大王的警告"}, {"type": "paragraph", "contents": [{"verseNum": 1, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶和華如此說：「你下到猶大王的宮中，在那裏說這話， "}, {"verseNum": 2, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "說：『坐大衛寶座的猶大王啊，你和你的臣僕，並進入城門的百姓，都當聽耶和華的話。 "}, {"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶和華如此說：你們要施行公平和公義，拯救被搶奪的脫離欺壓人的手，不可虧負寄居的和孤兒寡婦，不可以強暴待他們，在這地方也不可流無辜人的血。 "}, {"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "你們若認真行這事，就必有坐大衛寶座的君王和他的臣僕百姓，或坐車或騎馬，從這城的各門進入。 "}, {"verseNum": 5, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "你們若不聽這些話，耶和華說：我指着自己起誓，這城必變為荒場。』 "}, {"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶和華論到猶大王的家如此說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "我看你如基列，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "如黎巴嫩頂；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "然而，我必使你變為曠野，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "為無人居住的城邑。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "我要預備行毀滅的人，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "各拿器械攻擊你；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他們要砍下你佳美的香柏樹，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "扔在火中。"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "contents": [{"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "「許多國的民要經過這城，各人對鄰舍說：『耶和華為何向這大城如此行呢？』 "}, {"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "他們必回答說：『是因離棄了耶和華－他們神的約，事奉敬拜別神。』」"}]}, {"type": "heading", "heading": "關於約哈斯"}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "不要為死人哭號；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "不要為他悲傷，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "卻要為離家出外的人大大哭號；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "因為他不得再回來，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "也不得再見他的本國。"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "contents": [{"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 11, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "因為耶和華論到從這地方出去的猶大王約西亞的兒子沙龍，就是接續他父親約西亞作王的，這樣說：「他必不得再回到這裏來， "}, {"verseNum": 12, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "卻要死在被擄去的地方，必不得再見這地。」"}]}, {"type": "heading", "heading": "關於約雅敬"}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 12, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "那行不義蓋房、行不公造樓、"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "白白使用人的手工不給工價的有禍了！"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "他說：我要為自己蓋廣大的房、寬敞的樓，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "為自己開窗戶。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "這樓房的護牆板是香柏木的，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "樓房是丹色油漆的。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 15, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "難道你作王是在乎造香柏木樓房爭勝嗎？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 15, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "你的父親豈不是也吃也喝、"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 15, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "也施行公平和公義嗎？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 15, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "那時他得了福樂。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 15, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "他為困苦和窮乏人伸冤，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "那時就得了福樂。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "認識我不在乎此嗎？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "這是耶和華說的。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 17, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "惟有你的眼和你的心專顧貪婪，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 17, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "流無辜人的血，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 17, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "行欺壓和強暴。"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "contents": [{"verseNum": 17, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 18, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "所以，耶和華論到猶大王約西亞的兒子約雅敬如此說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 18, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "人必不為他舉哀說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 18, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "哀哉！我的哥哥；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 18, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "或說：哀哉！我的姊姊；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 18, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "也不為他舉哀說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 18, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "哀哉！我的主；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 18, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "或說：哀哉！我主的榮華。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 18, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 19, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "他被埋葬，好像埋驢一樣，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 19, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "要拉出去扔在耶路撒冷的城門之外。"}]}, {"type": "heading", "heading": "關於耶路撒冷百姓的命運"}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 19, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 20, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "你要上黎巴嫩哀號，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 20, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "在巴珊揚聲，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 20, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "從亞巴琳哀號，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 20, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "因為你所親愛的都毀滅了。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 20, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 21, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "你興盛的時候，我對你說話；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 21, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "你卻說：我不聽。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 21, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "你自幼年以來總是這樣，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 21, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "不聽從我的話。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 21, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 22, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "你的牧人要被風吞吃，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 22, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "你所親愛的必被擄去；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 22, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "那時你必因你一切的惡抱愧蒙羞。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 22, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "你這住黎巴嫩、在香柏樹上搭窩的，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "有痛苦臨到你，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "好像疼痛臨到產難的婦人，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "那時你何等可憐！"}]}, {"type": "heading", "heading": "神審判哥尼雅"}, {"type": "paragraph", "contents": [{"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 24, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶和華說：「猶大王約雅敬的兒子哥尼雅，雖是我右手上帶印的戒指，我憑我的永生起誓，也必將你從其上摘下來， "}, {"verseNum": 25, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "並且我必將你交給尋索你命的人和你所懼怕的人手中，就是巴比倫王尼布甲尼撒和迦勒底人的手中。 "}, {"verseNum": 26, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "我也必將你和生你的母親趕到別國，並不是你們生的地方；你們必死在那裏， "}, {"verseNum": 27, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "但心中甚想歸回之地，必不得歸回。」"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 27, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 28, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 哥尼雅這人是被輕看、破壞的器皿嗎？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 28, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "是無人喜愛的器皿嗎？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 28, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他和他的後裔為何被趕到不認識之地呢？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 28, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 29, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "地啊，地啊，地啊，當聽耶和華的話！"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 29, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 30, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶和華如此說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 30, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "要寫明這人算為無子，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 30, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "是平生不得亨通的；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 30, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "因為他後裔中再無一人得亨通，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 30, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "能坐在大衛的寶座上治理猶大。"}]}]}